Alarko Holding AS (ALARK)  said its unit in
 Kazakhstan  won a $98 million tender for the rehabilitation of a
lake and water treatment, according to a statement to the
 Istanbul Stock Exchange  after the market close yesterday.  To contact the reporter on this story:
